title: NASA releases first color image from James Webb Space Telescope
summary: A deep field of distant galaxies, some dating back to the first billion years after the Big Bang, is the first full-color image to come from the James Webb Space Telescope.

title: Webb telescope peers deeper into the universe than ever before
summary: The world got its deepest ever look into the distant universe Monday with the release of the first full-color science image from the James Webb Space Telescope, revealing thousands of faint galaxies shining like lampposts in a patch of speck of sky the size of a grain of sand held at arm’s length.

title: Webb’s first image reveals fine details of galaxies from billions of years ago
summary: "This telescope is one of humanity's great engineering achievements."

title: President Biden Reveals First Image from NASA’s Webb Telescope
summary: President Joe Biden released the first full-color image from NASA’s James Webb Space Telescope Monday, during a public event at the White House in Washington.

title: Biden revela la primera imagen del telescopio Webb de la NASA
summary: El presidente Joe Biden hizo pública el lunes la primera imagen a todo color del telescopio espacial James Webb de la NASA, durante un acto público en la Casa Blanca en Washington.
